                <h3 class="s-work__sub s-work__sub--large">Figchat</h3>

                <p>Talk to your teammates directly inside a Figma frame. There’s no third-party servers or setup required, simply select the frame you want to comment on and chat away. <a class="c-work__out-link" href="https://www.figma.com/community/plugin/836358953686653979/Figchat"
                        target="_blank"><span>Figchat</span></a> renders all your comments as items within Figma itself.</p>

                <p>Figma already has a commenting system, but Figchat was created for those situtations where you need the designs and the conversation working in tangent with one another.</p>

